    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<pre><code>对Latex的学习主要参考了刘海洋的《Latex入门》，下面将用勾股定理的pdf进行实操。使用的软件是Visual Studio Code,通过LaTeX Workshop 插件来实现Latex。</code></pre><a id="more"></a><figure class="highlight livescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">%勾股定理</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\documentclass[UTF8]&#123;ctexart&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">%------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\title&#123;杂谈勾股定理&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\author&#123;Zhangsan\\Peking&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\date&#123;\today&#125;</span>                      % <span class="string">\today</span> 输出的是电脑的当日的时期</span><br><span class="line">%以上信息仅是对文章信息提前申明，得通过<span class="string">&#x27;\maketitle&#x27;</span>输出，maketitle的输出格式是固定的</span><br><span class="line">%  <span class="string">&#x27;/&#x27;</span>是转义字符；<span class="string">&#x27;//&#x27;</span>为换行</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\bibliographystyle&#123;plain&#125;</span>          % <span class="string">&#x27;\bibliographystyle&#x27;</span> 声明参考文献格式</span><br><span class="line">% <span class="string">\begin</span> 以上部分都称为导言区（premble）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">%<span class="string">&#x27;\begin&#x27;</span> 与 <span class="string">&#x27;\end&#x27;</span> 之间为pdf的输出内容</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\begin&#123;document&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\maketitle</span>                         %输出文章信息(前文定义的)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\tableofcontents</span>                   %输出目录</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\section&#123;勾股定理在古代&#125;</span>            %开始新一节</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\section&#123;勾股定理的近代形式&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">\bibliographystyle&#123;math&#125;</span>           %从文献数据库math中获取文献信息，并输出</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="string">\end&#123;document&#125;</span> </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="/2021/01/10/Latex%20study1/%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E5%9B%BE.jpg" class title="This is an image">]]></content>
    
    
